    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required level. Test conditions factor achieves Gradation 1 against a required Gradation 2; this shortfall is accepted because static compression-bending under ASTM F1717 is the primary regulatory acceptance mode, the model is used solely for this loading scenario, and the experimental validation directly covers the intended use. Overall credibility sufficient for Medium model risk, Medium model influence, Medium decision consequence COU.",
